- New optional Audio Monitor lets you hear played notes with a built-in
  SoundFont instrument, directly from Input settings.
- Audio Monitor volume now has an exact percentage slider for fine control.
- MIDI device setup now uses clearer wording for both Bluetooth and wired USB
  connections.
- Device status icons now reflect transport type more accurately when connected.
- Improved compatibility for wired MIDI devices when Bluetooth permissions are
  unavailable.
